'''Kendriya Vidyalaya IIT Kanpur''' is a school situated in the [[IIT Kanpur]] campus, [[Kanpur]] in the Indian state of [[Uttar Pradesh]]. It was established in 1965 and is part of the [[Kendriya Vidyalaya]] system of schools. It has classes from grades I to XII.

== History ==
In 1965, IIT Kanpur was granted two bungalows with Shri D.S. Bajpai as the founding principal. The initial enrollment was 60 for VI to IX. 

==Academics==
The school offers class VI to XII, each with five sections. A secondary wing offers classes from I to V.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kviitkanpur.org/index.php|work=Introduction to Kendriya Vidyalaya, IIT Kanpur|accessdate=3 May 2014}}</ref> Kedriya Vidyalaya follows the curriculum set by the Central Board of Secondary Education ([[Central Board of Secondary Education|CBSE]]) and (ISC).

*

==Achievements==
During the initial years a number of meritorious students enrolled. KVS students are accepted by prestigious institutions including Indian Institutes of Technology and [[All India Institutes of Medical Sciences]]. 

Anurag Kaithal, Joyant Mandal and Palash Katiyar received [[KVPY]] scholarships funded by [[Department of Science and Technology (India)|Department of Science and Technology]]. Abhishek Srivastav tok 6th in the Junior Math Olympiad in the year 2011. Students won medals at national level in sport including [[tennis]], [[badminton]], [[cricket]] and [[Athletics (sport)|athletics]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Achievements |url=http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=kvpy |accessdate=30 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502013328/http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=kvpy |archivedate= 2 May 2014 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Olympiads |url=http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=olympiads |accessdate=30 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502015015/http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=olympiads |archivedate= 2 May 2014 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sports |url=http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=gamesandsports |accessdate=30 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502015017/http://www.kviitkanpur.org/innerpage.php?pagename=gamesandsports |archivedate= 2 May 2014 |df= }}</ref>

